name: Let The Sea Set You Free
raw_text:
=== TOUR START: Let The Sea Set You Free ===
Let The Sea Set You Free
8 hours of fun, activity & adventure!
Experience the very best of the Whitsundays on board this premium and beloved day tour!
is a fast power catamaran in the Whitsundays and is here to take you on the ride of your life!
The ultimate day trip that includes North and South Whitehaven Beach
Snorkel in the colourful fringing reefs of the Great Barrier Reef Marine Park
Visit Hill Inlet Lookout for the best views of the swirling silica sands
Cruise along at a speedy 25 knots, maximising your time to explore
Buffet lunch, wetsuits, snorkel gear, and paddleboards included
Please note that on public holidays, a $20 per adult and $10 per child surcharge applies to all tickets. Please see our
for more information on which dates this surcharge applies to.
=== TOUR END: Let The Sea Set You Free ===
